	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "instagram-clone-api",
		"name": "Instagram Clone API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for Instagram Mini Clone\n\n## Setup Instructions\n\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Create an environment with the following variables:\n   - `base_url`: http://localhost:5000/api\n   - `token`: (will be set automatically after login)\n3. Run the Signup or Login request first to get your token\n4. The token will be automatically saved to the environment\n\n## Authentication\n\nMost endpoints require authentication. Use the token from login/signup in the Authorization header as:\n`Bearer {{token}}`",
